snippet.title: Batography - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Play as a curious bat on his mission to take a full fledged photo of the moon. Run, Climb, Glide and Snap your way through an array of obstacles while interacting with the cheeky characters in the neighbourhood. Can you collect all the moon cakes?

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3351430/Batography/
